<paragraph id="IAS19_BC229" base="F16152348" principles="no"><paranum>BC229</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IAS 19"/><data name="paranum" value="BC229"/></prolog><body><p id="IAS19_P1600">The amendments made in 2011 improve the required disclosures about the amount, timing and uncertainty of future cash flows in the following respects:</p><ol id="IAS19_L0194" base="F16152350" type="lower-alpha"><li><li_value>(a)</li_value> <p id="IAS19_P1601" base="F16152351">information about asset&#x2011;liability matching strategies (<xref id="IAS19_X1100" base="F16231035" href="IAS19_gBC230-BC234.dita#IAS19_gBC230-BC234">paragraphs BC230&#x2013;BC234</xref>);</p></li><li><li_value>(b)</li_value> <p id="IAS19_P1602" base="F16152353">sensitivity analysis (<xref id="IAS19_X1101" base="F16231036" href="IAS19_gBC235-BC239.dita#IAS19_gBC235-BC239">paragraphs BC235&#x2013;BC239</xref>); and</p></li><li><li_value>(c)</li_value> <p id="IAS19_P1603" base="F16152355">information about the funding and duration of the liability (<xref id="IAS19_X1102" base="F16231037" href="IAS19_gBC240-BC243.dita#IAS19_gBC240-BC243">paragraphs BC240&#x2013;BC243</xref>).</p></li></ol></body></paragraph>